CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,FA 62-year-old man from Somerset has
OL,7,Fbeen sharing his experience of
OL,8,Fepilepsy, to raise awareness of the
OL,9,Fhidden impact the condition can have
OL,10,Fon memory.
OL,12,FVincent Smyth lives in Weston-super-
OL,13,FMare with his wife Carolynne, but for
OL,14,Fthe last ten years he has been unable
OL,15,Fto remember major life events,
OL,16,Fincluding his mother's funeral and his
OL,17,Fchildren's graduations.
OL,19,FHe now wants more people to understand
OL,20,Fthe varied symptoms that can be caused
OL,21,Fby epilepsy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,FVincent said: "There are several
OL,7,Fimpacts. The most problematic,
OL,8,Fcertainly for myself, is around
OL,9,Fmemory. The other impacts are around
OL,10,Funsteadiness of my feet and my ability
OL,11,Fto navigate.
OL,13,F"It's extremely frustrating. There's
OL,14,Falso elements of it which are quite
OL,15,Fsad, and then there are elements that
OL,16,FI would describe as ironically
OL,17,Fpositive.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,F"I struggle to or have no memory of my
OL,7,Fmother's funeral, which happened 5 or
OL,8,F6 years ago. I cannot remember at all
OL,9,Fthe graduation ceremonies for either
OL,10,Fof our children.
OL,12,F"There are a number of other key
OL,13,Fevents in life which are just like
OL,14,Fthat, that I have no memory of.
OL,16,F"Those memories, they don't come and
OL,17,Fgo. They are gone. Those memories have
OL,18,Fgone forever."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,F"We've gone to cities like Florence. I
OL,7,Fknow we've been there. We've talked
OL,8,Fabout it many times, but I have no
OL,9,Factual recollection whatsoever of
OL,10,Fbeing there.
OL,12,F"It's very tough for the family
OL,13,Fbecause we're unable to share the
OL,14,Fspecific things and to talk about the
OL,15,Fthings we did together."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,FVincent's symptoms started appearing a
OL,7,Fdecade ago but it took 8 years to be
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with temporal lobe epilepsy.
OL,9,FHe is now on medication which helps
OL,10,Fwith some symptoms, but the memory
OL,11,Floss persists.
OL,13,FCarolynne Smyth said: "We don't have
OL,14,Fany shared memories anymore. We go out
OL,15,Fand we do things, we go on holidays or
OL,16,Fwe see places, but Vincent doesn't
OL,17,Fremember it. So all those
OL,18,Fconversations of what we did together,
OL,19,Fwhere we've been, funny things that
OL,20,Fmay have happened on those days, it's
OL,21,Fall gone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,F"That can be quite a lonely place, to
OL,7,Fnot have those shared memories.
OL,9,F"I went through a long time of
OL,10,Fdocumenting everything we did with
OL,11,Fphotographs and posting a load of
OL,12,Fstuff on Facebook, and so that the
OL,13,Fmemories would come back up thinking
OL,14,Fthat it would jog his memory. But it's
OL,15,Fgone.
OL,17,F"I think had had we be more aware that
OL,18,Fit could be epilepsy, we would have
OL,19,Fgot the diagnosis and the medication a
OL,20,Flot quicker.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,FVincent is supporting Epilepsy
OL,7,FAction's Missing Memories campaign
OL,8,Fwhich shines a light on the lesser
OL,9,Fknown impact epilepsy can have on
OL,10,Fmemory and daily life.
OL,12,FNew polling data from the charity
OL,13,Ffound that nearly 7 in 10 people with
OL,14,Fepilepsy say the condition affects
OL,15,Ftheir everyday memories. It also found
OL,16,Fthat more than 1 in 5 say it has
OL,17,Faffected major life moments.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,FChantal Spittles from Epilepsy Action
OL,7,Fsaid: "Everyone's epilepsy is really
OL,8,Fdifferent. It is often obviously very
OL,9,Ffrequently associated with seizures.
OL,10,FThat's what we typically think when we
OL,11,Fthink of epilepsy.
OL,13,F"But people can also have other
OL,14,Fseizure types, where the electrical
OL,15,Fsignals are getting mixed up in the
OL,16,Fbrain and that causes memory problems.
OL,18,F"That can be incredibly frustrating,
OL,19,Fnot only having to deal with seizures,
OL,20,Fbut then dealing with those memory
OL,21,Fimpacts.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781161487
OL,3,CSomerset man says epilepsy left him
OL,4,Cunable to remember major life events
OL,6,F"It's really important that we have
OL,7,Fthat understanding so we can help
OL,8,Fpeople.
OL,10,F"We have lots of support groups and a
OL,11,Fhelpline because we know that for
OL,12,Fpeople experiencing frequent seizures
OL,13,Fand then memory problems and all the
OL,14,Fthings that come with that they can
OL,15,Foften feel very isolated."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
